Phase 9 done — pluggable persistence providers + stubbed payment hooks. Hosting is
generalized into a `persistence provider` interface that mirrors the video-provider
pattern: a Registry + BasePersistenceProvider whose `put(file) -> { ref, scheme,
gateway?, permanent? }`, one module per provider in docs/src/persist/. Four
providers ship: arweave (DEFAULT, ar://, pay-once permanent — uploads via a
user-funded Irys/Turbo/bundler endpoint, or routes through the payment hook),
pinning (ipfs://, Pinata JWT / web3.storage), seedbox (magnet:, in-tab WebTorrent
+ optional always-on seedbox POST), s3 (https, presigned/PUT). All tokens are
user-supplied (provider config), kept ONLY in the browser (localStorage
p2present:persist:<id>), never committed. Payment hooks for "Make permanent" are
STUBBED in docs/src/persist/payments.js: a documented adapter boundary
(window.__P2_PAYMENTS = { stripe, onchain }) with PaymentNotConfiguredError +
TODO markers for the Stripe (fiat) and on-chain-rent rails — no secrets in the
repo; SERVICE.md "#make-permanent" explains how to wire each. ar:// is a real
transport now: resolve.js (isArweave/arweaveGatewayUrls → arweave.net, ar-io.net)
+ manifest.js (resolveSrc, deck expansion, loadPresentation, timing) so produced
refs actually play; Builder deck dropdown + inferProtocol learn ar://. The Host
page (docs/host/) was rebuilt around the registry: a provider picker renders each
provider's config fields dynamically, uploads, surfaces the reference (with a
scheme tag, gateway preview, permanent/always-on badges), hands it to the Builder
via the existing p2present:hosted list, and shows the payment-wiring note instead
of crashing when Arweave has no endpoint. Tests: 45/45 app unit (ar:// transport +
manifest normalisation + mock-upload per scheme: pinata/web3storage→ipfs://,
s3→https query-strip, arweave→ar://, arweave no-endpoint→PaymentNotConfiguredError,
wired-rail-still-needs-endpoint, seedbox→magnet + always-on) + 23/23 Worker +
101/101 smoke (host picker has all 4, Arweave default + Make-permanent payment-stub
note, pinning pin mock → ipfs:// + builder handoff, seedbox trackers prefilled) @
390/780/1280, 0 real console errors, assets 200, static-only, light deps. Docs:
HOSTING (provider table + Arweave/S3 sections + always-on seedbox + payment note),
SERVICE (#make-permanent wiring), SPEC (4 transports + provider note), README,
ROADMAP (v1/v1.1 shipped, v2 layer shipped + paid rail pending), DOCS, AUTHORING.
Deployed live (Pages 200; src/persist/*.js + host serving). Live:
https://ibeezhan.github.io/p2present/host/
